{"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/99732", "repository_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust", "labels_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/99732/labels{/name}", "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/99732/comments", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/99732/events", "html_url": "https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/issues/99732", "id": 1317293890, "node_id": "I_kwDOAAsO6M5OhE9C", "number": 99732, "title": "Combination of no_mangle and used attribute leads to mangled symbol name", "user": {"login": "Tiwalun", "id": 859555, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjg1OTU1NQ==", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/859555?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/Tiwalun", "html_url": "https://github.com/Tiwalun", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/Tiwalun/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/Tiwalun/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/Tiwalun/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/Tiwalun/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/Tiwalun/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/Tiwalun/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/Tiwalun/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/Tiwalun/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/Tiwalun/received_events", "type": "User", "site_admin": false}, "labels": [{"id": 650731663, "node_id": "MDU6TGFiZWw2NTA3MzE2NjM=", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/labels/C-bug", "name": "C-bug", "color": "f5f1fd", "default": false, "description": "Category: This is a bug."}], "state": "closed", "locked": false, "assignee": null, "assignees": [], "milestone": null, "comments": 2, "created_at": "2022-07-25T19:50:48Z", "updated_at": "2022-07-26T05:57:57Z", "closed_at": "2022-07-26T05:57:57Z", "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR", "active_lock_reason": null, "body": "<!--\r\nThank you for filing a bug report! \ud83d\udc1b Please provide a short summary of the bug,\r\nalong with any information you feel relevant to replicating the bug.\r\n-->\r\n\r\nI tried this code:\r\n\r\n```rust\r\n#[no_mangle]\r\n#[used]\r\npub static exported_static: u32 = 10;\r\n```\r\n\r\nThis is compiled into a binary. I expect that the symbol is part of the binary, and that the name is not mangled, due to the `no_mangled` attribute. Example nm output of a correct case:\r\n\r\n```\r\n...\r\n00000240 T exported_static\r\n...\r\n```\r\n\r\n\r\nInstead, the symbol name gets mangled:\r\n\r\n```\r\n...\r\n00000240 t _ZN18hifive_flashloader15exported_static17hef539998df4d12acE\r\n...\r\n```\r\n\r\n\r\nHowever, if I remove the `#[used]` attribute, then it works correctly:\r\n```rust\r\n#[no_mangle]\r\npub static exported_static: u32 = 10;\r\n```\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n### Meta\r\n\r\nThis only occurs on the nightly compiler:\r\n\r\n ```\r\nrustc 1.64.0-nightly (7fe022f5a 2022-07-24)```\r\n\r\n On stable rustc 1.62.1, the symbol does not get mangled.\r\n", "closed_by": {"login": "Tiwalun", "id": 859555, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjg1OTU1NQ==", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/859555?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/Tiwalun", "html_url": "https://github.com/Tiwalun", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/Tiwalun/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/Tiwalun/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/Tiwalun/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/Tiwalun/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/Tiwalun/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/Tiwalun/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/Tiwalun/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/Tiwalun/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.